name: growing pains Recovery Party with RRILEY

metadata.description:
"Everything is just as it should be."

This token is a little gift to commemorate your presence at the very special 'growing pains' Recovery Party with RRILEY at SPHERE on 8 December 2022! A restorative afternoon celebrating the launch of RRILEY's 'growing pains' Music Video over Recovery Sessions including infrared saunas, cold plunges and sensory deprivation float tanks.

Stay tuned for an upcoming special edition of NFTs by RRILEY.
